.683 0.0785 2.2991C0.1696 1.6318 0.3956 1.1176 0.7566 0.7566C1.1176 0.3956 1.6318 0.1696 2.2991 0.0785C2.683 0.0261 3.4262 -0 4.5287 0L6.7098 0C7.2636 0 7.6421 0.0086 7.8456 0.0257C8.1956 0.0551 8.4945 0.1278 8.7423 0.2439C8.9901 0.36 9.2374 0.543 9.4841 0.7931C9.6274 0.9384 9.8764 1.2238 10.2309 1.6491L11.8313 3.5697C12.0849 3.874 12.2464 4.0995 12.3158 4.2462C12.3413 4.3002 12.3643 4.3553 12.3847 4.4114C12.4057 4.469 12.4238 4.5275 12.4391 4.5868C12.4797 4.744 12.5 5.1039 12.5 5.5L11.9167 5.5ZM8.1667 1.2707L8.1667 2.2864C8.1666 2.9774 8.1811 3.4291 8.2101 3.6413C8.2413 3.8699 8.3 4.0274 8.3863 4.1137C8.4726 4.2 8.6301 4.2587 8.8587 4.2899C9.0709 4.3189 9.5226 4.3334 10.2136 4.3333L10.949 4.3333C10.9443 4.3277 10.9397 4.3222 10.9351 4.3166L9.3346 2.396C8.8002 1.7548 8.4378 1.3896 8.2475 1.3004C8.225 1.2899 8.1981 1.28 8.1667 1.2707Z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span>send_data.py</code> 拖进去，Commit</li>
<li>完成</li>
</ol>
<h2>方式二：命令行 git（推荐，方便后续改代码直接推）</h2>
<p>先在 GitHub 网页建好空仓库（同上第 1、2 步，但<strong>不勾</strong> README），然后：</p>
